<td class="mbox-image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/Nutshell.png" width="30" height="30" /></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>This page in a nutshell:</b> Readers must be able to check that Wikipedia articles are not just made up. This means that all quotations and any material challenged or likely to be challenged must be attributed to a reliable, published source using an <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:INCITE" title="Wikipedia:INCITE" class="mw-redirect">inline citation</a>.</td>
</tr>
</table>
